{"tid":554602,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"加藤鷹認證雞屎忽可拍AV：Ｄ奶夠大了","createTime":"2018-02-08T16:30:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-09T15:40:58.000Z","uid":157545,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"38c87cf984e5e3ab85b5a0281f9511be2dbd404c","tid":554602,"uid":157545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T16:30:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180207/640_95476bf8acedc14c121a22c2747c88eb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180207%2F640_95476bf8acedc14c121a22c2747c88eb.jpg&h=f53bef09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n藝人雞排妹今趕回台灣與加藤鷹一起參加《抓GO樂》遊戲記者會，雞排妹說日本大雪，所以有此軟體很方便，加藤鷹則說不怕娃娃難夾，因他手指靈活沒問題。 雞排妹說在日北太冷就不會出門，加藤鷹則說喝酒後最愛去夾娃娃！享受夾到的樂趣跟成果。<br />\n<br />\n而被問到在日本的情況，雞排妹說現在就是念語言學校，在兩個月才會再回台，情人節也是自己過，不過她透露有奇怪豔遇，「我跟我朋友在六本木附近街上走，結果有3個日本男人看起來就是喝過酒的，就過來問我要不要一起去喝一杯，我一直說不要，他們還是糾纏我，最後是賣沙威瑪的中東朋友幫我解圍，我也邀他們去警局他們才罷休」。<br />\n<br />\n雞排妹跟加藤鷹也被媒體問到合作的可能，加藤鷹表示：「其實雞排妹在現在的領域上工作就很好了，不是每個人都適合去拍ＡＶ。」此時雞排妹心虛地說，最近瘦3公斤（44公斤，156公分），胸部這麼小（現在是30D）可以嗎？加藤鷹笑說，「完全沒問題，夠大了」。<br />\n<br />\n兩人在現場也被問看到花蓮強震的心情，雞排妹說，昨天有被小驚嚇，加藤鷹說：「昨晚住在11樓真的很晃，一想到日本311大地震台灣人給予日本那麼多幫助與捐款，真的很感動，我跟雞排妹都應該為災區加油！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180207/640_497baa4f8821e68f8a48d48c2eee878b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180207%2F640_497baa4f8821e68f8a48d48c2eee878b.jpg&h=04a48ba8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180207/640_4fb03f4c3186d7661b92dda9277cb06b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180207%2F640_4fb03f4c3186d7661b92dda9277cb06b.jpg&h=7211eb8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180207/640_e41aea652412ec751ba9f4ff62d689c2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180207%2F640_e41aea652412ec751ba9f4ff62d689c2.jpg&h=134a94b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180207/640_be113cc67d7e5218592f5e90b3810905.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180207%2F640_be113cc67d7e5218592f5e90b3810905.jpg&h=72bb0863&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6564640dcd194c1143cfdc5de65be8cd0697fb72","tid":554602,"uid":3698,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T19:10:37.000Z","msg":"昨晚住在11樓真的很晃<br />\n<br />\n大力後入雞排妹仲晃"},{"pid":"8cf84386c604a8caf8def13644770628dd472fb9","tid":554602,"uid":157545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T01:41:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af3d48731c432d3058d4e6c7eea054db28c2343e","tid":554602,"uid":54104,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T04:00:25.000Z","msg":"當年有一套偽 AV <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f215f5bd2e73446c7ea4767a53077f7b5d9ae7cf","tid":554602,"uid":76605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af3d48731c432d3058d4e6c7eea054db28c2343e","tid":554602,"uid":54104,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T04:00:25.000Z","msg":"當年有一套偽 AV <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T15:40:58.000Z","msg":"link呢"}]}